{"word":"Fish","slug":"fish","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Fish</b> Creation of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=22'>Gen 1:22</a><br/> Appointed for food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=3'>Gen 9:3</a><br/> Clean and unclean<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=12'>Lev 11:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=10'>Deu 14:10</a><br/> Taken with:<br/> - Nets<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=9&verse=12'>Ecc 9:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=35&chapter=1&verse=17'>Hab 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=21'>Mat 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=6'>Luk 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=8'>Joh 21:8</a> <br/> - Hooks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=19&verse=8'>Isa 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=2'>Amo 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=27'>Mat 17:27</a> <br/> - Spears<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=41&verse=7'>Job 41:7</a> <br/> Ponds for:<br/> - In Heshbon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=7&verse=4'>Son 7:4</a> <br/> - In Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=19&verse=10'>Isa 19:10</a> <br/> Traffic in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=16'>Neh 13:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=13'>Joh 21:13</a><br/> Broiled<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=13'>Joh 21:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=42'>Luk 24:42</a><br/> Miracles connected with:<br/> - Jonah swallowed by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=17'>Jon 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=2&verse=10'>Jon 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=40'>Mat 12:40</a> <br/> - Of the loaves and fishes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=19'>Mat 14:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=36'>Mat 15:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=6'>Luk 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=17'>Luk 9:17</a> <br/> - Coin obtained from mouth of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=27'>Mat 17:27</a> <br/> - Great draught of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=7'>Luk 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=6'>Joh 21:6</a> <br/> - Furnished to the disciples by Jesus after His resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=42'>Luk 24:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=13'>Joh 21:13</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=10'>Eze 47:10</a>"}]}